# The current reference viewer requires no runtime environment variables.
#
# Deployment automation may supply these outside the repository:
# VERCEL_TOKEN=
# VERCEL_ORG_ID=
# VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=
#
# Future browser-visible values must use the framework's public prefix only when
# they are genuinely safe to expose. Never place provider credentials, database
# URLs, or private scientific-data tokens in a VITE_* / NEXT_PUBLIC_* variable.
